{"tid":1689611,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[文宣新建議] 文宣撚請入","createTime":"2019-11-03T02:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T07:03:40.000Z","uid":199793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82d356236f45ed88889bfff5c6106fe72b709110","tid":1689611,"uid":199793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"而家嘅文宣方向主要都係列左五大訢求、活動宣傳、警黑的事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要令運動持續，當然要正中香港人以錢為重的心態，所以必須大大力宣傳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「攬炒對各位香港人的好處」</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人(特別五、六十後)都覺得攬炒負面，對佢地無著數，但咁諗就大錯特錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隋左迫政府回應，更加可以令商店做大量減價促銷，香港人就可以大買便貨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓價又跌，雖然跌幅唔大，但比起政府D垃圾樓價辣椒更有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以支持本土小店發展，有多D選擇，唔洗焗住消費俾大財團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多好處，唔係唔支持攬炒下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ceb43964b866306f5333d41870b51b254263ed","tid":1689611,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死黑警從來無認真關心過香港人條命<br />\n講緊被死亡個案，佢仲係度冷笑、當笑話"},{"pid":"4c1126f8df0776b45bac9b4fba2969